name: .$01 File Extension
summary: Learn about .$01 files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Text file that contains output "piped" to it by a DOS program; often used for debugging programs; can be viewed in a text editor.

content: The ".$01" extension may be a dollar sign followed by other numbers as well. I.e. ".$02," ".$03," etc.
